        {
            "+content": "The story takes place in a trading city Ert'Aria. Leicester Maycraft is an item engineer belonging to an adventurer guild \"Oasis\". One night, he is at a party with his friends to see a meteor stream on the rooftop of a chapel. One meteor grazes them and hits the steeple of the chapel. There he finds a secret room and a sleeping girl. The girl wakes up and says \"You must be my father\". The encounter with the mysterious girl brings an unexpected adventure to Leicester.",
